---
import Layout from "../layouts/main.astro";

const heroImage = "/assets/images/projects/zash-hero-card.jpg"; 
const miroImg = "/assets/images/projects/Zash--process board Miro.avif";
const wireframeImg = "/assets/images/projects/Zash-Wireframes iteration.avif";
const dashboardImg = "/assets/images/projects/Zash-Dashboard.avif";
const leadImg = "/assets/images/projects/Zash-Lead management.avif";
const campaignsImg = "/assets/images/projects/Zash-campaigns screen.avif";
const creationImg = "/assets/images/projects/Zash-campaign creation 3.avif";
const sequenceImg = "/assets/images/projects/Zash-campaign sequence.avif";
const chatImg = "/assets/images/projects/Zash-Conversation and bot chat screen.avif";
const responsiveImg = "/assets/images/projects/Zash-Responsive Screens.avif";
---

<Layout title="Zash">
  <div class="w-full bg-white  transition-colors duration-300">
    <header class="relative h-[85vh] min-h-[600px] w-full flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden bg-slate-900">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-slate-900/50 z-10"></div>
      <img
        src={heroImage}
        alt="Zash Hero"
        class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover object-top opacity-50 animate-slow-zoom"
        transition:name="project-image-/zash"
      />

      <div class="relative z-20 text-center max-w-5xl px-6 mt-20">
        <span class="inline-block py-1 px-3 rounded-full bg-white/10 border border-white/20 text-white text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 backdrop-blur-md">
          UI Design Case Study
        </span>
        <h6 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-6 tracking-tight leading-tight">
          Zash
        </h6>
        <p class="text-1xl md:text-2xl text-slate-200 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed font-light">
          A sales engagement platform powered by AI, helping businesses streamline and automate outbound outreach efforts, from lead generation to conversion.
        </p>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="border-b border-gray-100  bg-white ">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-400  uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Role</h3>
            <p class="font-medium text-gray-900 ">UI Designer</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-400  uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Timeline</h3>
            <p class="font-medium text-gray-900 ">2 weeks</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-400  uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Stack</h3>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-100  rounded text-xs font-medium text-gray-600 ">Figma</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <button
              disabled
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full py-3 bg-gray-200  text-gray-500  rounded-xl font-bold cursor-not-allowed shadow-sm"
            >
              No Live Link
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="ml-2 opacity-50"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10"></path></svg>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 space-y-24">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900  mb-8">
          The Challenge
        </h2>
        <p class="text-l text-gray-600  leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Many businesses, from SMEs to large enterprises, face the challenge of efficiently conducting outbound sales and business development. Building and executing high-converting sales campaigns is time-consuming and requires deep expertise. 
        </p>
        <p class="text-l text-gray-600  leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Existing solutions often lack the ability to fully automate these processes and provide truly personalised messaging.
        </p>
        <p class="text-l text-gray-600  leading-relaxed mb-12">
          As a Ground-Up MVP, my responsibility was to collaborate with a cross-functional team of PMs and Devs, alongside the founder, to create a storyboard outlining essential features, before building wireframes and iterating towards the final UI solution.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900  mb-8">
          A First Look
        </h2>
        <div class="mb-16">
          <p class="prose prose-l text-gray-600  mb-8 max-w-full">
            Before diving into the process, here is a sneak peek at the final responsive solution we arrived at to solve the complex challenges of automated outbound sales.
          </p>
          <img src={responsiveImg} alt="Responsive Solution Sneak Peek" class="w-full max-h-[700px] object-cover object-top rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 " />
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900  mb-8">
          Discovery & Ideation
        </h2>
        <div class="mb-16">
          <p class="prose prose-l text-gray-600  mb-8 max-w-full">
            Every successful product starts with a solid foundation. I collaborated with the founder and cross-functional teams in Miro to storyboard the core user journeys, map out the required AI integrations, and define the MVP feature set before pushing a single pixel.
          </p>
          <img src={miroImg} alt="Miro Process Board" class="w-full max-h-[700px] object-cover object-top rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 " />
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900  mb-8">
          Iterative Wireframing
        </h2>
        <div class="mb-16">
          <p class="prose prose-l text-gray-600  mb-8 max-w-full">
            Moving from abstract concepts to tangible layouts, I rapidly prototyped low-fidelity wireframes. This iterative process allowed the team to align on the core navigation and data hierarchy early on, ensuring the complex AI sales flows were logically structured. I always make sure my project files are organised so that collaboration is seamless, work is efficient, and user flows are easy to follow.
          </p>
          <img src={wireframeImg} alt="Wireframe Iterations" class="w-full max-h-[700px] object-cover object-top rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 " />
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- The Solution -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900  mb-8">
          The Solution & Features
        </h2>

        <!-- 1. Dashboard -->
        <div class="mb-16">
          <h3 class="text-1xl font-bold text-gray-900  mb-4">
            1. Comprehensive Dashboard
          </h3>
          <p class="prose prose-l text-gray-600  mb-8 max-w-full">
            A centralized, bird's-eye view where users can instantly monitor active campaigns, track lead conversion metrics, and evaluate overall performance.
          </p>
          <img src={dashboardImg} alt="Dashboard Design" class="w-full max-h-[700px] object-cover object-top rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 " />
        </div>

        <!-- 2. Lead Management -->
        <div class="mb-16">
          <h3 class="text-1xl font-bold text-gray-900  mb-4">
            2. Lead Management
          </h3>
          <p class="prose prose-l text-gray-600  mb-8 max-w-full">
            A robust interface designed to handle bulk data. Users can effortlessly import, sort, and organize their leads, ensuring the right prospects are funneled into the right AI sequences.
          </p>
          <img src={leadImg} alt="Lead Management" class="w-full max-h-[700px] object-cover object-top rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 " />
        </div>

        <!-- 3. AI Campaign Creation -->
        <div class="mb-16">
          <h3 class="text-1xl font-bold text-gray-900  mb-4">
            3. AI Campaign Creation & Sequencing
          </h3>
          <p class="prose prose-l text-gray-600  mb-8 max-w-full">
            The beating heart of Zash. I designed an intuitive flow that guides users through generating AI-powered, multi-channel outreach campaigns. The visual sequence builder allows users to map out complex email, SMS, and social media touchpoints with ease.
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <img src={campaignsImg} alt="Campaigns Screen" class="w-full max-h-[700px] object-cover object-top rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 " />
            <img src={creationImg} alt="Campaign Creation" class="w-full max-h-[700px] object-cover object-top rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 " />
            <img src={sequenceImg} alt="Campaign Sequence" class="w-full max-h-[700px] object-cover object-top rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 " />
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 4. Conversational AI -->
        <div class="mb-16">
          <h3 class="text-1xl font-bold text-gray-900  mb-4">
            4. Conversational AI
          </h3>
          <p class="prose prose-l text-gray-600  mb-8 max-w-full">
            To drive conversions autonomously, I designed a dedicated chat interface where the conversational AI can qualify leads and nurture prospects in real-time.
          </p>
          <img src={chatImg} alt="Conversational AI Chat" class="w-full max-h-[700px] object-cover object-top rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 " />
        </div>

        <!-- 5. Responsive Design -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-1xl font-bold text-gray-900  mb-4">
            5. Responsive Design
          </h3>
          <p class="prose prose-l text-gray-600  mb-8 max-w-full">
            While primarily a desktop-first enterprise tool, I ensured the layouts scaled elegantly to mobile devices, allowing sales teams to monitor campaigns on the go.
          </p>
          <img src={responsiveImg} alt="Responsive Screens" class="max-w-full h-auto object-contain rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 " />
        </div>

      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  @keyframes slow-zoom {
    0% { transform: scale(1); }
    100% { transform: scale(1.05); }
  }
  .animate-slow-zoom {
    animation: slow-zoom 20s linear infinite alternate;
    transform-origin: top center;
  }
</style>
